data.name: load_ds_button.ToolTip
data.value:
Opens directory browser to select the Dataset pool.
To properly load the Dataset at once, just select the Parent folder and click OK.
NOTE: the Experiment subpaths must match the numeration: 11, 21, 31 ... [n]1

data.name: label_OORExp.ToolTip
data.value:
Click to show the list of Experiments for which the peaks were outside the current import control boundaries.
TIP: reset the application with different import limits or check for broken spectra in the current dataset.

data.name: checkBoxInactives.ToolTip
data.value:
Check this Checkbox to display only the Experiments in the Dataset that were marked as Inactives by the CSP MCC algorithm.
Checking both of the Actives/Inactives checkboxes will reset the view to all the Spectra.

data.name: checkBoxActives.ToolTip
data.value:
Check this Checkbox to display only the Experiments in the Dataset that were marked as Actives by the CSP MCC algorithm.
Checking both of the Actives/Inactives checkboxes will reset the view to all the Spectra.
